Manteiner: Gianluca Mattei <gianluca.mattei@unifi.it>
Author: Gianluca Mattei
Description: Methods annotateDMRs() to retrieve annotations for DMRs and scoreAnnotatedDMRs() to assign a score to the annotated DMRs. Method annotateEhancers() is used to associate enhancers to genes. Method plotDMRs() used to visualize the annotated regions.
